name: Meline
headerTaglineThree: Cute English teacher and languages genius
aboutpara: The website is a gift made by Changrui to his good friend Melineeee as her birthday gifts.

WordsFromChangrui.ShortWords: Meline my friend, Congrats on another trip around the sun!🎂 I hope this day is full of cake, memories, and fun:). I wish ur everyday as as special as you are☀️
WordsFromChangrui.description: I may make u a pig🐷  with magic if you don't behave
